      • format

        String format(String fmt)
        Deprecated. 
        Return the version formated as string with the format specified as fmt. It replace in fmt: - %M by the major number of the version - %m by the minor number of the version - %r by the revision number of the version - %c by the classifier of the version - %b by the build number of the version
        Parameters:
        fmt, - string used as format
        Returns:
        the version formated as string
